---
title: Transferencia Presencial y Excepción Manual
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Admin
    participant BFF
    participant API as API pública
    participant App as api:app Orchestrator
    participant Billing as Billing Core
    participant Physical as Physical Core

    BFF->>API: POST /api/v1/billing/payments/{paymentId}/proof
    API->>Billing: Guardar comprobante privado
    Billing->>Billing: Payment permanece PENDING

    Admin->>BFF: Aprobar transferencia
    BFF->>API: POST /api/v1/billing/admin/payments/{paymentId}/approve
    API->>App: ApproveManualPayment(paymentId)
    App->>Billing: Verificar movimiento y snapshot
    App->>Physical: Convertir CapacityHold idempotentemente
    alt Capacidad asignada
        Physical-->>App: CapacityAssignment[]
        App->>Billing: Payment COMPLETED
        App->>Billing: Purchase CAPACITY_ASSIGNED
        App-->>API: Compra confirmada
    else Movimiento externo confirmado y capacidad fallida
        Physical-->>App: CAPACITY_UNAVAILABLE
        App->>Billing: Payment REQUIRES_MANUAL_REVIEW
        App->>Billing: Purchase EXCEPTION y auditoría
        App-->>API: 409 MANUAL_REVIEW_REQUIRED
    else Sin movimiento válido
        App->>Physical: Liberar hold
        App->>Billing: Payment FAILED / Purchase CANCELLED
        App-->>API: Pago rechazado
    end

    Note over Admin,Physical: No se ejecuta reembolso, reemplazo ni compensación automática

